<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer lieber her <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan>, als
                                <expan>meist<ex>er</ex></expan> Hans,
                            <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> czü sant Laurenczen, her heim kom, der
                        sagt uns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew wol, wie ir uns
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> bey im <expan>embot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het,
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        ersamkeit czemal <expan>fleizziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew, daz
                        ir uns bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gege<ex>n</ex>wertigen</expan> von disen lewffen
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, was ir davon
                        wisset, als vil ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> füglich
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> sey cze
                            <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> sünderlich <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                        Viti.</ab>
</div>
